в”Ӯ ## Executive Summary                                                         в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                              в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ The Windows 10 system has been compromised by an APT actor who has           в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ established persistent backdoor access through two malicious processes. The  в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ compromise involves command and control (C2) communications with an external в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ server.                                                                      в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                              в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ ## Timeline of Events                                                        в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                              в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ - **2018-09-05 14:27:55**: ftusbsrvc.exe process established listener on     в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ port 33001                                                                   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ - **2018-09-06 17:17:20**: license_ctrl.e process established listener on    в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ port 5682                                                                    в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ - **Multiple timestamps**: Ongoing C2 communications with 172.16.4.10:8080   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                              в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ ## Indicators of Compromise                                                  в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                              в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ **Malicious Processes:**                                                     в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ - license_ctrl.e (PID 1716) - Listening on port 5682                         в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ - ftusbsrvc.exe (PID 4916) - Listening on port 33001                         в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                              в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ **Network Indicators:**                                                      в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ - C2 Server: 172.16.4.10:8080                                                в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ - Backdoor Ports: 5682, 33001                                                в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                              в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ ## Persistence Mechanisms                                                    в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                              в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ The malicious processes maintain persistent access through:                  в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ - Network listeners on ports 5682 and 33001                                  в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ - Ongoing C2 communications with external server 172.16.4.10                 в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                              в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ ## Recommendations                                                           в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                              в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 1. **Immediate Actions:**                                                    в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ    - Isolate the compromised system from the network                         в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ    - Block communications to 172.16.4.10                                     в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ    - Terminate processes PID 1716 (license_ctrl.e) and PID 4916              в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ (ftusbsrvc.exe)                                                              в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                              в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 2. **Investigation:**                                                        в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ    - Examine parent processes and execution paths for these malicious        в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ binaries                                                                     в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ    - Search for additional persistence mechanisms                            в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ    - Analyze network logs for full scope of C2 communications                в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                              в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 3. **Remediation:**                                                          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ    - Complete system rebuild recommended                                     в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ    - Implement enhanced network monitoring for similar indicators            в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                              в”Ӯ
